data.description: Beautiful 3 bed, 2 full bath Brick home, sitting on almost an acre and a half!! Walk into the living area and you're greeted with a real wood burning fire place and gorgeous cathedral ceilings. The kitchen has a breakfast nook or dining room. Fenced in back patio with plenty of shade overlooking a huge back yard!! This home has an attached garage and comes with a 9x10 storage/well she. 8 minutes away from the recently remodeled Mallard Golf Club, 3470 Morganfield Dr. Sellers are motivated! Home will be sold “As Is”. Sellers will not pay for any repairs to the home. All measurements +/-.
